    "updated_at": "2023-06-13T07:57:45Z",
    "body": "> IMHO there is something going on with zoxide and bg jobs.\r\n\r\nAs mentioned by @davidkna, the hook used by zoxide to update the scores when the current directory is changed registers as a background job. I'm not sure why changing the order of initialization fixes it, which is why I created this issue here to see if we could arrive at a more reliable solution.",
