    "body": "zoxide prepends its hook to `$PROMPT_COMMAND`, which is why it's getting run before the `jobs` command. We need to check how Starship avoids overriding hooks in `$PROMPT_COMMAND`, that should tell us why it is dependent on order of initialization.",
